{
  "stem": "23506.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the end, she starts-- and she starts to fry it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, you know, are you sure this is fresh meat?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's so dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Horse meat is a much darker, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see, she-- and we made her eat it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and she didn't know that she was eating treif horse meat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and-- but the other, the liver and those things, she never wanted to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What became of your mother?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- when the Germans surrounded our ghetto, when I run away with my brother, they were caught.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went into hiding-- my mother, my sister, and my father, and two other neighbors-- in the attic under the [? eaves. ?] Somebody hid in that place, was a deserter in World War I who was never caught.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when my parents went into it, one man was lived in our house, [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shaiya ?] was his name, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shaiya ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zinger, ?] I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when he saw that my parents-- somehow they knew, because my father and the other member brought water to the-- to the hiding place so that they will have enough water.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said like this to my father, Herschel, if you don't let me in with my family, nobody's going to go in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what were they supposed to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They let him in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was such a-- the place, it was only made for a few.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They laid there like sardines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When one wanted to move, all of them had to move.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they stayed there, I think, three or six weeks, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of those.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the ghetto was-- was clear of Jews, the Germans were going to get all those people from the hiding places.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
